---
const stats = [
	{ value: "26+", label: "Years of Experience" },
	{ value: "Millions", label: "Recovered for Clients" },
	{ value: "Free", label: "Initial Consultation" },
];
---

<section class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:px-8 lg:py-28">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[320px_1fr] lg:items-start lg:gap-16">
			<!-- Attorney photo -->
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[320px] lg:mx-0">
				<img
					src="/Eric_Blank_01.jpg"
					alt="Eric R. Blank — Personal Injury Attorney, Las Vegas"
					width="600"
					height="900"
					loading="lazy"
					class="h-auto w-full rounded-xl"
				/>
			</div>

			<!-- Bio -->
			<div>
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-brand-navy uppercase">
					Meet Your Attorney
				</p>
				<h2
					id="about-heading"
					class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-navy sm:text-4xl"
				>
					Eric R. Blank
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-brand-gold sm:text-xl">
					Former Insurance Defense Attorney. Now Fighting For You.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-pretty text-gray-600">
					<p>
						For years, Eric Blank worked for the insurance companies. As an insurance
						defense attorney, he was hired to evaluate injury claims, find their weak
						points, and keep payouts low. Today he stands on the opposite side — using
						that insider knowledge to fight for the injured people those same companies
						try to underpay.
					</p>
					<p>
						With more than 26 years of legal experience, Eric has seen the claims process
						from every angle. Before devoting his practice to injury victims, he defended
						insurance carriers in court and served as general counsel for the local NBC
						and Fox television affiliates. Today his focus is singular: representing
						injured plaintiffs throughout Las Vegas and Clark County.
					</p>
					<p>
						Eric left insurance defense for a straightforward reason — he wanted his work
						to mean something. Helping injured people recover, rebuild, and hold the
						responsible parties accountable is what drives him. That's the work he does
						today, and he's recovered millions in verdicts and settlements doing it.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Stat callouts -->
				<dl class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 sm:gap-6">
					{
						stats.map((stat) => (
							<div>
								<dt class="sr-only">{stat.label}</dt>
								<dd>
									<span class="block text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy sm:text-3xl">
										{stat.value}
									</span>
									<span class="mt-1 block text-sm text-gray-500">{stat.label}</span>
								</dd>
							</div>
						))
					}
				</dl>

				<!-- CTA -->
				<a
					href="https://ericblanklaw.com/attorneys/eric-blank/"
					class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-gold px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-brand-navy transition-colors hover:bg-[#d1a63b]"
				>
					Read Eric's Full Bio
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
